&lt;p&gt;We are increasing our workforce in both clinical and administrative areas of the department. This is an exciting time for the unit and we welcome your application to become part of our team. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Sherwood Forest Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust is a progressive forward thinking trust renowned for innovative practice and development. We have pledged to offer every patient the best care provided by the best people in the best place. We have the ultimate blend of cutting edge technology, dedicated staff and innovative departments that together strive to achieve excellence and Quality for All.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you hold an NVQ3 in Care and are hard-working with good organisational skills, committed to providing high quality patient care with a passion for improving the patient experience we would love to hear from you.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
